4608.name: A Hallway

4611.name: Stairs going up to the livingroom.

4513.name: Casino Nights [West Slot Row]
description: You stand infont of the slot machine.  Pretty lights and colors
flash off it, and it makes buzzing noises at you.  Someone pumps in a
hefty amount of cash, and they pull the lever.  The machine whirls, as
the three wheels spin around, CERCHING the first one stops...
CERCHING...  The second one stops.  You stare at it, watching the
third wheel turn..  Waiting for it to strike...  CERCHING..  It hits,
and the someone looses out on the money.  The machine makes a cackling
noise.

marble walls, going around the whole lobby.  In the center, a large
white marble fountain stands, pouring fresh booze from the basement.
Around the edges of the bowls, gold lining shines in the Makou Gas
Lights.  To the west, the Elite Lounge can be found, large windows
overlooking the streets of Westbridge.  To the east is the main bar
of the casino.  To the south, is the fun.

description: You step into a large marble building. You see three lines
of people standing, waiting in line to talk to the person
behind the wall. The smell of fresh cut gold, silver and
platinum rings threw the air. Large square tables dot
the whole area, with small lambs and pens on them. You see
the banker behind his window, waiting for you to speak.

4610.name: Stairs going to the bathroom

4557.name: Room 1
description: The room is filled with curtains and cloths and silk.  A large bed sits

4602.name: A Hallway

description: This is the southern section of the lobby of Casino Nights.  It lies

4550.name: The Blue Moon Tavern
description: There are a flight of stairs leading down right here, into what looks
like to be a bar.  North large glass windows look out into the street.  From

fountain flow with the waters of the river.

4535.name: The Dancing Daemon Inn
description: You step into the the guest room section. The owner stands behind
a large desk, writing in the log book of travelers who have gone
by. You see 3 large keys directly behind him. Above you a large
glass skylight shines in the sky above. To the west is the
bar section of the inn.

4514.name: Casino Nights [Main Walk]
description: You stand on the Main Walk in the Casino.  All around you are the

slots stands before you, its large sum of money stands before you,
shall you pump your money into it, or walk away.

description: Smoke makes this room dark and quiet.  There are many people sitting around

chairs are placed all around the room.  A large hot tub sits to one side of
the room.

4553.name: The Blue Moon Tavern
